SUMMARY:Ship Happens
LOCATION:The Libra Theatre Cafe\, London
DESCRIPTION:A slice of life set in the strangest of environments — a crui
 se ship. A floating city of eccentric characters and unexpected locations\,
  from the jail buried deep in the hull to the chandeliered ballroom ten dec
 ks above. Each show throws a melange of guests and crew together\, bound fo
 r a destination not yet known\, on a ship that won't exist tomorrow. Drama 
 is certain\, comedy is guaranteed. Because out at sea ... Ship Happens. We 
 are a team made up of highly experienced improvisers and stage actors that 
 have all trained and regularly perform at The Free Association in London as
  well as acclaimed performing arts schools including RADA and East 15.\nMor
 e info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/ship-happens/
